text:
The food was packed quite efficiently and fast :D
It taste amazing too

Very nice friendly staff
Loga! Definitely the best choice during lunch time
Always a nice pit stop during cycling. Spacious, new and clean restaurant. Staff are helpful and attentive, esp to kids. Going out of their way to help them to carry the food trays to the tables.

We have been coming to this BK at Home Team Bedok every week for the past 1yr. The service here is excellent despite understaff most of the time. Mr Loga and his colleagues are exceptionally hardworking and efficient with good working attitudes.

We enjoyed our breakfast very much. :)
Lovely atmosphere and warm and friendly staff. Came on a weekend and they were working diligently with a big smile even though there were a lot of people. Big compliments to Loga!
